    <body>
      <div xml:id="NA225-kiḷavi">
        <p type="edition">1. itu vaṉpuṟai (G1+2: vaṉpoṟai) yetiraḻintatu. 2. parattai talaimakaṭkup pāṅkāyiṉa vāyil (ET: vāyilkaḷ) kēṭpac colliyatūumām.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">1. This is being desolate in the face of consolation. 2. It is also what the other woman said so that the mediators who were close to HER would hear.</p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="NA225">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>            murukuṟaḻ muṉpoṭu kaṭuñciṉañ cerukkip</l>
<l>            poruta yāṉai veṇkōṭu kaṭuppa</l>
<l>            vāḻai yīṉṟa vaiyēntu koḻumukai</l>
<l>            melliyaṉ makaḷi rōti yaṉṉa</l>
<l>            pūvoṭu tuyalvaru mālvarai nāṭaṉai </l>
<l>            yirantō ruḷarko ṟōḻi tiruntiḻait</l>
<l>            toyyil vaṉamulai varivaṉap piḻappap</l>
<l>            pacanteḻu paruvara ṟīra</l>
<l>            nayantōrk kutavā nāriṉ mārpē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Is there someone, friend, who begged</l>
<l rend="indent">the man from a land of big mountains,</l>
<l rend="indent3">where</l>
<l rend="indent2">the sharp upright rich bud brought forth by the plantain,</l>
<l rend="indent3">resembling the white tusk of the elephant that had fought,</l>
<l rend="indent4">elated by fierce anger, with a strength close to Murukaṉ’s,</l>
<l rend="indent2">comes to swing together with flowers,</l>
<l rend="indent2">as the hair of soft-natured women:<note place="foot">If this elaborate structure with double simile is rightly attributed to Kapilar, as T.V.G. affirms, one feels entitled to expect that it is supposed to mean something. But what?</note></l>
<l rend="indent">for [his] bondless chest that doesn’t help those that long [for it]</l>
<l rend="indent">to end the fading [and] the rising suffering,</l>
<l rend="indent2">while the beautiful breasts with sandal paste<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">toyyil</term>: this is explained by T.V.G. to be not sandal paste, but a coloured paste used to paint ornaments on women’s breasts.</note> [and]</l>
<l rend="indent2">perfect jewels lose the beauty of [their] streaks?</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
